            Sophia Florsch: 17-year-old F3 crash driver on 'new chapter'
            Sophia Florsch has left hospital after a horrific high-speed Formula 3 crash more than a week ago in the Macau Grand Prix.And after taking "some time to get over it", the 17-year-old says she's excited for a "new chapter".Follow Newsbeat on Instagram, Facebook and Twitter.Listen to Newsbeat live at 12:45 and 17:45 every weekday on BBC Radio 1 and 1Xtra - if you miss us you can listen back here.
                
